Coega IDZ&ldquo;The metals and manufacturing industrial sector of the Coega IDZ will soon roll out three investment projects, with the first project&rsquo;s site handover planned for April 2017,&rdquo; says Sadick Davids, CDC business development manager - metal and manufacturing. The following are the three investment projects currently in the process of implementation: a R650m manufacturing cement grinding plant,&nbsp;a R71m ready mix concrete plant, anda R350m gas cylinder plant. The investment projects are said to accumulatively see over 401 direct jobs created and 2472 construction jobs.